  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal Profile, pending signature)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package conforms to the Minimal profile; a package hash is present but the digital signature has not yet been applied — the signature workflow is pending final review board approval. All 13 credibility factors are assessed or scoped. Package integrity cannot be cryptographically verified until the signature field is populated.",
