    "rationale": "The credibility assessment package for COU2 VAD hemolysis prediction is accepted for submission to the regulatory review queue under the Minimal profile. Six of thirteen credibility factors remain not-assessed and all assessed factors show achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5. The package is accepted for process tracking purposes only — not as evidence of model credibility sufficiency. Digital signature is pending completion of the institutional signature workflow; the sha256 hash is recorded to support future integrity verification once the signature is applied.",
